{"tid":1897361,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"伊朗已經係另一個武漢","createTime":"2020-02-25T16:28:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T17:13:05.000Z","uid":30688,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ac328fcc8407aa241d52e21b3b02d96f27fda14a","tid":1897361,"uid":30688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T16:28:31.000Z","msg":"隔離小國巴林竟然一日加左21單<br />\n<br />\n另外鄰國如科威特，伊拉克等都分別有5單同8單。一定唔係官方公佈既95單可以造成咁既傳播。恐怕伊朗國內已經如傳言所講有數以千計既感染。<br />\n<br />\n再加上中東人既衛生情況....整個伊斯蘭世界淪陷真係遲早既事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n亞洲有支那同南韓，歐洲有意大利，中東有伊朗... 係差非洲同美洲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldometers.info/coronavirus/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldometers.info%2Fcoronavirus%2F&d=JcMWRxryG4qpJesfomKpWPSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=f17faf9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldometers.info/coronavirus/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CDNDiRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCDNDiRG.png&h=850216ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7d11b9b203a7a7ffb1abde44dc65be884c3cd1c","tid":1897361,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T16:29:48.000Z","msg":"國際要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（求人手置頂）【twitter 極度要人】英國議會提出香港議案；美國歐洲議員為桂民海發聲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1897293\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1897293</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"960f9a92bfc55d63229afe835545375d302670be","tid":1897361,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T16:35:32.000Z","msg":"隻手出面摸摸摸之用手食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\